 changes too often, find the parent component that defines it and wrap that definition in useCallback.",["537"],"'Done' is defined but never used.","jsx-a11y/anchor-is-valid","The href attribute is required for an anchor to be keyboard accessible. Provide a valid, navigable address as the href value. If you cannot provide an href, but still need the element to resemble a link, use a button and change it with appropriate styles. Learn more: https://github.com/jsx-eslint/eslint-plugin-jsx-a11y/blob/HEAD/docs/rules/anchor-is-valid.md","React Hook useEffect has missing dependencies: 'count', 'done', 'ifdone', and 'isShowConfirm'. Either include them or remove the dependency array. If 'ifdone' changes too often, find the parent component that defines it and wrap that definition in useCallback.",["538"],"no-dupe-keys","Duplicate key 'Search'.","ObjectExpression","unexpected","React Hook React.useEffect has missing dependencies: 'data' and 'total'. Either include them or remove the dependency array. You can also do a functional update 'setData(d => ...)' if you only need 'data' in the 'setData' call.",["539"],"'Grid' is defined but never used.","eqeqeq","Expected '===' and instead saw '=='.","BinaryExpression",{"desc":"540","fix":"541"},{"desc":"542","fix":"543"},{"desc":"544","fix":"545"},{"desc":"546","fix":"547"},{"desc":"548","fix":"549"},{"desc":"550","fix":"551"},{"desc":"552","fix":"553"},{"desc":"554","fix":"555"},{"desc":"556","fix":"557"},{"desc":"558","fix":"559"},{"desc":"558","fix":"560"},{"desc":"561","fix":"562"},{"desc":"563","fix":"564"},{"desc":"565","fix":"566"},{"desc":"567","fix":"568"},"Update the dependencies array to be: [loadTopMenu]",{"range":"569","text":"570"},"Update the dependencies array to be: [history, ready]",{"range":"571","text":"572"},"Update the dependencies array to be: [check]",{"range":"573","text":"574"},"Update the dependencies array to be: [loadTop]",{"range":"575","text":"576"},"Update the dependencies array to be: [cb, date]",{